   Web-Based Encyclopedia
                                            [nhtsa.gif]
   __________________________________________________________________

   NHTSA decided in 1996 to make FARS data easier to obtain by using
   Internet technology. This FARS Web-Based Encyclopedia offers a more
   intuitive and powerful approach for retrieving fatal crash information.
   __________________________________________________________________



